        <title>Camping trip checklist</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;When you head into the wild, trying to remember to pack everything you need is not an easy task. I always get to the campsite and realize that I forgot something. Here is a camping checklist for the adventurous:&lt;/p&gt;

